subject: Economy
question_en: What is the primary contributor to India's Gross Domestic Product (GDP)?
question_hi: भारत के ग्रॉस विक्रेता (GDP) का प्रमुख उपयोगी क्या है?
explanation_en: Services sector is the primary contributor to India's GDP. It contributes significantly to the country's economy by providing various services to the population and contributing to employment opportunities.
